parameters: Today was a wonderful day! I went to my favorite tree
by the village to draw. It has the biggest branches,
and I can sit under it for hours....
I brought my colored pencils and sketched all the
pretty flowers around the tree. The butterflies danced
in the sunlight, and I felt so happy.
But then, all of a sudden, the wind started to blow.
It got stronger and stronger, and the sky turned dark!
I watched as my drawings fluttered away like
little birds. I ran as fast as I could to catch them,
but they disappeared into the storm.
I was so scared! I ran home, and I think I left my
favorite hair bow behind. I hope it’s okay. I can’t
wait to go back tomorrow and see if I can find it!
